<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c3">{عَلَى النَّبِيِّ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٦]</span> كاف.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>{تَسْلِيمًا <span class="c2">(٥٦)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٦]</span> تام.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c3">{وَالْآَخِرَةِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٧]</span> جائز.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>{مُهِينًا <span class="c2">(٥٧)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٧]</span> تام،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«مبينًا»</span>؛ على استئناف ما بعده، وجائز إن عطف على ما قبله.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span><span class="c3">{مِنْ جَلَابِيبِهِنَّ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٩]</span> حسن،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«فلا يؤذين»</span>.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
